## Severity Guide

| Severity | Meaning |
|---|---|
| `CRITICAL` | Direct exploit path in production. Block deploy. |
| `HIGH` | Exploitable under realistic conditions or meaningful data exposure. Fix before prod. |
| `MEDIUM` | Hardening gap that raises risk without a direct exploit path. Fix this sprint. |
| `INFO` | Defence-in-depth improvement. Low immediate risk. |

